name: ZEUS
description: A Frog's Best Friend Zeus was brought to life by the iconic artist Matt Furie. He's the fun and loyal dog who hangs out with the Boys Club. He's teaming up with Pepe, Brett, Andy, and Landwolf to bring $ZEUS to Solana. Join Zeus and the rest of the gang to bring their chaotic misadventures to the blockchain. $ZEUS is a community-led and driven project. Liquidity is 100% burnt - Contract is fully renounced
